!                           Oxford University Press, 2nd Edition (2017)                           !
!                             doi: 10.1093/oso/9780198803195.001.0001                             !
!                             --------------------------------------                              !
!                               G. Macpherson, M. K. Borg, J. Reese                               !
!              Molecular Simulation, Taylor & Francis, 2007, 33 (15), pp. 1199-1212.              !
!                                 doi: 10.1080/08927020701730724                                  !
